  "description": "Closing the books transfers the balances of temporary accounts (revenues, expenses, dividends/draws) into [retained earnings](../terms/retained-earnings.md), resetting them to zero for the next period. This is the final step in the [accounting cycle](../concepts/accounting-cycle.md) before the post-closing trial balance.",
